## Interactive Charts

Interactive analysis is enhanced with advanced [Zoom](./zoom/) capabilities and [Range Buttons](./range-buttons/) for seamless time period navigation.

{% video videoSrc="resources/zoom.mp4" /%}

## Financial Chart types

The default chart type is [Candlestick](./candlestick-series/), with additional types like [OHLC](./ohlc-series/) and [Line](./line-series/) available from the [Toolbar](./financial-charts-toolbar#chart-type-selection) for versatile data visualisation.

